public class AutoGater
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.treestar.lib.core.PopulationPluginInterface

This test class illustrates the implementation of the External Population Algorithm plugin. It doesn't do anything useful, but attempts to show all the different types of return values that can be used by ExternalAlgorithmResults.
